    "One of the exciting features of ChatGPT is its ability to understand the context of a conversation and generate relevant responses (Choi et al., 2023).",
    "This model can adapt to various languages and conversational styles, making it useful in various communication applications.",
    "However, like all AI technology, ChatGPT has limitations, including a tendency to produce information that is not always accurate or produce inappropriate content in some cases.",
    "Therefore, the use of ChatGPT needs to be managed wisely and monitored to ensure ethical and beneficial use in various contexts (Dalalah & Dalalah, 2023: 1).",
